column5: Any updates on road construction on 17 fron the "SOO" to White River, 631 from White River to 11,and 11 to Geraldton. THANKS :cheers:

I just got back from Savant Lake and drove around Superior on 17. There is construction between Thunder Bay and White River (actually Marathon), but none between the Soo and White River. The rest I can't comment on.
